Polish immigrant/performer/serial divorcee, lived to an active 97.  I
highly recommend visiting her sprawling "Lotusland" garden in Santa
Barbara, California, most famous for its collection of cycads and other
ancient plants (make reservations months ahead of time of possible, a
limited number of visitors are allowed to keep peace with the
neighbors).

